,{"pid":"201e6d3c5e804f50ae7f970ac18dcdbbd4fd4301","tid":1537882,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"890c8398561bd8507f925f03e50dd1851c0ae310","tid":1537882,"uid":260195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"大專學生豁免做陪審團喎"},{"pid":"3c5ab3aa0439b2ed6ab8b43830ba8b22ca03bf69","tid":1537882,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:37:08.000Z","msg":"佢寄咗信俾我 係唔係好等人使？"},{"pid":"067c5a09957bd3c05979790556edb565b46a478b","tid":1537882,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add0a0f82f5fb9c999c84d2a7eaf365e40e46839","tid":1537882,"uid":277296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b39530e579f2f70938f1f8cab800293b8ad1ac","tid":1537882,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62bc16824fcc8234e0cbbd6c1ebec666b11bdda7","tid":1537882,"uid":277296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"廢老其實唔少都唔係大陸呀嬸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:38:21.000Z","msg":"要讀乜 等大家查定字典唔好讀錯"},{"pid":"6ca36692877bff721c2fc85c7d16125ebaa455de","tid":1537882,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s